$ SQL Developer: Tools -> Preferences -> Code Editor -> Completion Insight

Specify settings such as
  • Enabling of completion auto-popup in SQL Worksheet
  • Enabling of completion auto-popup in PL/SQL Editor
  • Popup Speed
  • Suppression of pop-ups for more than *n* matches
  • Automatic generation of column/table aliases
  • Enabling of semantic analysis info tip

